---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="mt-16 border-t border-ixporte-purple/20 bg-[#050008]">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Brand -->
      <div>
        <a href="/" class="inline-block">
          <img
            src="/logo-branca.png"
            alt="ixporte — Jornalismo Esportivo"
            class="h-12 w-auto"
            width="160"
            height="32"
          />
        </a>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-ixporte-white/50 leading-relaxed max-w-xs">
          Portal de jornalismo esportivo produzido por estudantes do curso de Jornalismo da UFSC.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Links -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-headline font-bold text-ixporte-crimson uppercase tracking-wider text-sm mb-4">Navegação</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li><a href="/reportagens" class="text-ixporte-white/50 hover:text-ixporte-white transition-colors duration-200">Reportagens</a></li>
          <li><a href="/copa-feminina-2027" class="text-ixporte-white/50 hover:text-ixporte-white transition-colors duration-200">Copa Feminina 2027</a></li>
          <li><a href="/especiais" class="text-ixporte-white/50 hover:text-ixporte-white transition-colors duration-200">Especiais</a></li>
          <li><a href="/sobre" class="text-ixporte-white/50 hover:text-ixporte-white transition-colors duration-200">Sobre</a></li>
          <li><a href="/contato" class="text-ixporte-white/50 hover:text-ixporte-white transition-colors duration-200">Contato</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Social -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-headline font-bold text-ixporte-crimson uppercase tracking-wider text-sm mb-4">Redes Sociais</h3>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <a href="https://instagram.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-ixporte-white/50 hover:text-ixporte-crimson transition-colors duration-200" aria-label="Instagram">
